Jenkins VM

SSH connection to AWS Instance or Webserver WM:
ssh-copy-id -i ~/.ssh/vm3 student@192.168.1.5

SSH connection to github repo:
eval $(ssh-agent -s)
ssh-add ~/.ssh/github
ssh -T git@github.com

Connect to DockerHub:
cat /home/student/Docker/password.txt | docker login --username olesyudin --password-stdin

Push container to DockerHub:
docker build -t password_generator:v1 .
docker tag password_generator:v1 olesyudin/password-generator:latest
docker push olesyudin/password-generator



AWS Instance or Webserver WM
Install:
sudo apt-get install -y apache2 docker.io

Change group for webserver:
cd /var/www
sudo chgrp -R student /var/www
sudo chmod -R g+rw /var/www

Add user to Docker group
sudo usermod -aG docker student

docker pull olesyudin/password-generator:latest
docker run -ti -d -p 8888:80 --name=password-generator olesyudin/password-generator:latest